Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:37.53,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\1c&H2E292C&\fs30\pos(316,660)\frz15.71}別管別人怎麼看！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有大家寫來互相加油的信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然紙上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但東鄉學姐幫大家畫了南瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太可怕了 這不是欺負人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦應該知道什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他們也說什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們也是這麼回答我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦又跟我們裝傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來大赦確實是一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我跟我有權交流的神官們問鷲鷲的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都搖頭說不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然會有大赦都不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我鬧了脾氣讓他們拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦的人就拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用這個去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼找…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在還能變身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 小魚乾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們看 鷲鷲的手機不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我手機的雷達 也沒有探測到鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲可能在一個出乎我們意料的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的意思是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牆的外面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉這麼脫線 的確可能跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以變成勇者去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變成勇者 還會為力量付出代價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說這次版本更新 沒有散花了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}簡直好到難以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 再怎麼更新系統 結果還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}害怕是當然的 我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 為了找到東鄉 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這和第一次的時候不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我作為社長 不希望大家輕易就變身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的確經歷過很多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果沒有勇者自我犧牲的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界已經毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦的做法只是不太恰當 但不能怪誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦向我保證 不會再隱瞞勇者系統的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當面聽過後 我決定相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以和以前不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次我願意接受 我會去找她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然不是很認識大赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是小園都這麼說了 我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐 我想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 別丟下社長一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也相信友奈和乃木你們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然有勇者社員失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同為社員就有責任去找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過要去牆外 就不知道會發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埼樹 先多吃點營養品補身子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次我吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們真是群好夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小園也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新版勇者系統中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開槽從一開始就是滿能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精靈可以張開護罩保護勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但使用護罩會消耗盛開槽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而盛開槽不能回復
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以在盛開槽滿的時候使用盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使用後會消耗全部盛開槽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開槽消耗完 精靈就不能張開護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這時受到攻擊就會有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是沒有散花的勇者系統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是像這樣把一切都說清楚比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 這樣就能做好心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事後打掃可能很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}犬神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牛鬼 好久不見 請多關照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 看不到前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它果然還是很黏姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}異端
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}諸行無常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}借踏一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再往前就唔啊啊啊了 大家多小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我打頭陣 園子在我背後支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小魚乾 別一個人衝太前面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}埼樹 今晚做特製烏龍麵給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我會滿心期待的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是這麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼看都不像是同個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷達上有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是東鄉 東鄉果然在牆壁外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們有機會 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到會這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是這個方向嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在那個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 鷲鷲好像就在那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…竟然變成了黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次碰上好久不見的人成了黑洞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}周圍有Vertex啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但要怎麼過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏偏挑這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝了 埼樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很厲害嘛 園子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被稱讚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣下去只會單方面被消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底要怎麼去東鄉那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐天船應該能到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天船…園子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼突然就盛開了 會沒有精靈保護的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我經歷過沒有護罩的時代 不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是去鷲鷲身邊的天船 大家都坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好帥的船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉園子你們幾個真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的才是最帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小園真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等著我吧 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位沒有暈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還什麼暈不暈的 感覺好不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡面究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們主動出擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道他們在保護這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去東鄉她那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們一定要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你一定要平安回來 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是社長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}礙事的傢伙交給我們解決
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡面什麼事都有可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿出氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}包在我身上 小園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 一口氣衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會讓你妨礙悠悠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}悠悠 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我必須到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}靈魂離體？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道…要是我倒在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的身體也會一直留在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園上了我們所在的國中後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就發生了大赦未曾預料到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我破壞了一部分結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導致外界火焰劇烈的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣下去 外界的火焰將吞噬世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦需要凍結迄今為止的反抗計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並著手打破現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是東鄉的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 你就在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有別的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要減弱火勢 必須舉行奉火祭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是將能聽到神之聲的巫女獻給外界的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請求天神原諒的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是西曆紀年結束時舉行過的獻祭儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在大赦供職的幾位巫女 被選作了活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但大赦的人告訴我 我也可以擔任這個角色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我同時擁有勇者的資格和巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是獨一無二的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼好煩惱的 是我讓結界開了洞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定要為此贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要友奈還有其他人平安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}犧牲我一個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要是消失了 友奈她們一定會來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以神樹大人 請不要讓她們這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉總是這麼固執
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然自己消去了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我跟你約好的 不會留下你一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 無論多少次我都會救你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然是那時見到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我這就救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這點痛算什麼 把東鄉放開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起回去吧 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了 這樣就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 你醒啦 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家…這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你睡了好幾天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你們救我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣下去 世界會被火…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們知道情況了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火勢已經趨於平穩 所以也不需要祭品了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道說有人代替我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 你好像被奪走了常人會死的生命能量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你也算完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你很頑強 所以還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後我們也及時趕到了 差不多這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好有好好鍛鍊過身體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醫生說你全身都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 安全啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦你完成使命囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然還得在醫院待上一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這下勇者社再次全員聚齊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明約好不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們卻忘了好幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才該道歉 讓你們這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法嘛 換成是我也會這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次碰上這種事 一定要跟我們商量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過就這樣扯平不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的確也忘記過你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但大家最後還是想起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖 乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告一段落啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以全員聚齊過聖誕 除夕和新年啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼全是玩的事啊
Comment: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:43.78,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}尊き勇者たち　一時の平和が来た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:57.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}何もかもすべてが　眠りにつく時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:10.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}戦った人　涙堪えた人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:21.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}朧げな夢が　迎えに来るでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:33.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}勇敢な人　涙零した人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:38.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今日はおやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:48.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}寝息を立てたら　夜が包み込む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:43.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}尊貴的勇者們 迎來了短暫的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:57.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}萬物沉寂 合上了迷濛的睡眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:10.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}那些戰鬥的人 噙住眼淚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:21.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}也將前往那片 朦朧的夢鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:33.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}那些無畏的人 灑下熱淚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:38.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今天好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:48.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}安心睡吧 深深的黑夜會包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太殘酷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是災難啊 災難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好像知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心別受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不能把他人捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐！
